<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BON 카드뉴스 워크플로우 — 본동물의료센터</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --g700:#4d6230; --g500:#617d3b; --g400:#7c9443; --g100:#b2ca75; --g50:#f8fbe8;
  --n600:#1d2432; --n500:#1d2744;
  --warm:#f6edd9; --acc:#f6d85d; --br:#8B6B4A;
  --div:#d5cbbf; --text:#504538; --sub:#7a8c6e; --strong:#1d2432;
  --r:12px;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{font-family:'Pretendard',-apple-system,sans-serif;background:#edeae3;color:var(--text);display:flex;min-height:100vh;}

/* SIDEBAR */
.sb{width:220px;min-height:100vh;background:var(--n600);display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;}
.sb-logo{padding:24px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);}
.sb-tag{display:inline-block;background:var(--g500);color:var(--g50);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;}
.sb-name{color:#fff;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.4;}
.sb-sub{color:var(--g100);font-size:11px;margin-top:3px;}
.sb-nav{padding:12px 0;flex:1;}
.nav-lbl{color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:12px 20px 4px;}
.nav-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 20px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;border-left:2px solid transparent;transition:.15s;text-decoration:none;}
.nav-item:hover{color:#fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);}
.nav-item.active{color:var(--acc);border-left-color:var(--acc);background:rgba(246,216,93,.05);font-weight:700;}
.sb-foot{padding:14px 20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);line-height:1.8;}

/* MAIN */
.main{margin-left:220px;flex:1;}
.topbar{background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--div);padding:0 28px;height:52px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;}
.tb-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--strong);}
.tb-right{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;}
.chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;}
.chip-g{background:var(--g50);color:var(--g500);border:1px solid rgba(97,125,59,.2);}
.chip-a{background:rgba(246,216,93,.15);color:#7a6000;border:1px solid rgba(246,216,93,.3);}
.chip-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g500);}

.content{padding:24px 28px 60px;}

/* SECTION LABEL */
.sec{margin:32px 0 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.sec-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g500);flex-shrink:0;}
.sec-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--strong);}
.sec-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);}
.sec-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--div);}

/* PIPELINE */
.pipeline{background:var(--n600);border-radius:var(--r);padding:24px 28px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:4px;}
.pipeline::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 50%,rgba(97,125,59,.2) 0%,transparent 60%);pointer-events:none;}
.pipe-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.pipe-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:10px 0;position:relative;}
.pipe-item+.pipe-item{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);}
.pipe-num{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--n500);border:1.5px solid rgba(178,202,117,.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--acc);flex-shrink:0;}
.pipe-txt{}
.pipe-ttl{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:2px;}
.pipe-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--g100);opacity:.8;}
.pipe-tag{margin-left:auto;flex-shrink:0;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(97,125,59,.25);color:var(--g100);}

/* GRID 2 */
.grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.grid3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}

/* CARD */
.card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--div);overflow:hidden;}
.card-hd{padding:14px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.card-hd.dark{background:var(--n600);}
.card-hd.green{background:var(--g500);}
.card-hd.olive{background:var(--g700);}
.card-hd.warm{background:var(--warm);border-bottom:1px solid var(--div);}
.card-hd.subtle{background:var(--g50);border-bottom:1px solid var(--div);}
.card-hd.navy{background:var(--n500);}
.card-ico{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;}
.card-n{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.07em;margin-bottom:2px;}
.on-d{color:var(--g100);} .on-g{color:rgba(248,251,232,.65);} .on-w{color:var(--g500);}
.card-ttl{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;}
.c-w{color:#fff;} .c-d{color:var(--strong);}
.card-bd{padding:14px 18px;}

/* STEP LIST */
.slist{list-style:none;}
.slist li{display:flex;gap:8px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f3ef;font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:#555;}
.slist li:last-child{border:none;}
.si{width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--g50);color:var(--g500);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.slist strong{display:block;font-weight:700;color:var(--strong);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:1px;}
.slist span{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);}

/* TAGS */
.tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;padding:10px 18px;border-top:1px solid #f5f3ef;}
.tag{padding:2px 9px;border-radius:100px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;background:var(--g50);color:var(--g500);border:1px solid rgba(97,125,59,.15);}
.tag.dk{background:var(--n500);color:var(--g100);border-color:transparent;}
.tag.ac{background:rgba(246,216,93,.15);color:#7a6000;border-color:rgba(246,216,93,.3);}

/* COLOR PALETTE */
.palette{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--div);padding:18px 20px;}
.sw-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin-top:8px;}
.sw{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--div);}
.sw-dot{width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;}
.sw-name{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--strong);}
.sw-hex{font-size:9px;color:var(--sub);font-family:monospace;}
.palette-warn{font-size:10px;color:#b94040;margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid var(--div);}

/* FONT TABLE */
.font-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px;}
.font-table th{padding:8px 12px;background:var(--g50);color:var(--g500);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--div);}
.font-table td{padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f3ef;color:var(--text);}
.font-table tr:last-child td{border:none;}
.fw-preview{font-family:'Pretendard',sans-serif;font-size:15px;}

/* CONTENT TYPE */
.ctype-card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--div);overflow:hidden;}
.ctype-hd{padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;}
.ctype-hd.ct-center{background:var(--n600);color:var(--g100);}
.ctype-hd.ct-equip{background:var(--g700);color:var(--g50);}
.ctype-hd.ct-news{background:var(--g500);color:#fff;}
.ctype-hd.ct-disease{background:var(--g50);color:var(--g700);}
.ctype-bd{padding:10px 14px;}
.pages{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin-bottom:7px;}
.pg{padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;}
.pg-d{background:var(--n600);color:var(--g100);}
.pg-w{background:var(--warm);color:var(--br);border:1px solid var(--div);}
.pg-g{background:var(--g500);color:#fff;}
.pg-m{background:var(--g50);color:var(--g700);border:1px solid rgba(97,125,59,.2);}
.pg-wh{background:#fff;color:var(--strong);border:1px solid var(--div);}
.ctype-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.6;}
.ctype-meta b{color:var(--strong);}

/* TOOL CARDS */
.tool-card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--div);padding:16px;text-align:center;transition:.15s;}
.tool-card:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.07);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.tool-card.rec{border-top:3px solid var(--g500);}
.tool-ico{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.tool-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--strong);margin-bottom:4px;}
.tool-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.55;}
.rec-badge{display:inline-block;margin-top:8px;background:var(--g50);color:var(--g500);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid rgba(97,125,59,.2);}

/* CHECKLIST */
.checklist-wrap{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--div);padding:18px 20px;}
.cklist{list-style:none;}
.cklist li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:9px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f3ef;font-size:12px;color:var(--text);}
.cklist li:last-child{border:none;}
.ck{width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:4px;border:1.5px solid var(--g500);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:9px;color:var(--g500);cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;}
.ck:hover{background:var(--g50);}
.ck.done{background:var(--g500);border-color:var(--g500);color:#fff;}

/* CTA BANNER */
.cta{background:var(--n600);border-radius:var(--r);padding:22px 24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:4px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.cta::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-30px;right:-30px;width:160px;height:160px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(97,125,59,.3) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%;}
.cta-l{position:relative;}
.cta-eye{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--g100);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;}
.cta-ttl{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin-bottom:4px;}
.cta-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--g100);opacity:.8;}
.cta-r{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;text-align:right;position:relative;}
.cta-contact{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);}
.cta-contact span{color:var(--acc);font-weight:700;font-size:12px;}

@media(max-width:780px){
  .sb{display:none;}
  .main{margin-left:0;}
  .grid2,.grid3{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<div class="sb">
  <div class="sb-logo">
    <div class="sb-tag">Brand Guide v2.0</div>
    <div class="sb-name">BON Animal<br>Medical Center</div>
    <div class="sb-sub">카드뉴스 워크플로우</div>
  </div>
  <nav class="sb-nav">
    <div class="nav-lbl">Workflow</div>
    <a class="nav-item active" href="#pipeline">📋 전체 프로세스</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#steps">🔧 단계별 상세</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#brand">🎨 브랜드 시스템</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#types">📱 콘텐츠 유형</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#tools">⚡ 디자인 도구</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#checklist">✅ 체크리스트</a>
  </nav>
  <div class="sb-foot">
    Pretendard 서체 적용<br>
    SKILL.md v2.0 기준<br>
    2026.06 업데이트
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN -->
<div class="main">
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="tb-title">인스타그램 카드뉴스 제작 워크플로우</div>
    <div class="tb-right">
      <span class="chip chip-g"><span class="chip-dot"></span>Pretendard</span>
      <span class="chip chip-a">v2.0</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <!-- PIPELINE -->
    <div id="pipeline" class="sec" style="margin-top:4px;">
      <div class="sec-dot"></div><div class="sec-title">전체 프로세스</div>
      <div class="sec-line"></div><div class="sec-sub">6단계</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pipeline">
      <div class="pipe-list">
        <div class="pipe-item">
          <div class="pipe-num">01</div>
          <div class="pipe-txt"><div class="pipe-ttl">디자인 시스템 개발</div><div class="pipe-sub">Claude Design 신규 프로젝트 생성 · 토스 구조 참고</div></div>
          <span class="pipe-tag">Setup</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-item">
          <div class="pipe-num">02</div>
          <div class="pipe-txt"><div class="pipe-ttl">스타일 가이드 · 스킬 적용</div><div class="pipe-sub">bon-animal-card-news SKILL.md 추가 지침 업로드</div></div>
          <span class="pipe-tag">SKILL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-item">
          <div class="pipe-num">03</div>
          <div class="pipe-txt"><div class="pipe-ttl">브랜드 로고 · 컬러 적용</div><div class="pipe-sub">로고 첨부 → 3계층 토큰 등록 (Primitive → Semantic → Component)</div></div>
          <span class="pipe-tag">Brand</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-item">
          <div class="pipe-num">04</div>
          <div class="pipe-txt"><div class="pipe-ttl">핀터레스트 레퍼런스 적용</div><div class="pipe-sub">레퍼런스 3–5장 + 슬라이드별 텍스트 초안 동시 첨부</div></div>
          <span class="pipe-tag">Reference</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-item">
          <div class="pipe-num">05</div>
          <div class="pipe-txt"><div class="pipe-ttl">디자인 시안 개발</div><div class="pipe-sub">Claude Design 자동 생성 → 컬러·폰트 검수 → 수정 반복</div></div>
          <span class="pipe-tag">Design</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-item">
          <div class="pipe-num">06</div>
          <div class="pipe-txt"><div class="pipe-ttl">피그마 · 캔바 파일 전송</div><div class="pipe-sub">Figma MCP(정밀편집) 또는 Canva MCP(SNS 발행) 선택 출력</div></div>
          <span class="pipe-tag">Export</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STEP DETAIL -->
    <div id="steps" class="sec">
      <div class="sec-dot"></div><div class="sec-title">단계별 상세</div>
      <div class="sec-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-hd dark">
          <div class="card-ico">🏗️</div>
          <div><div class="card-n on-d">STEP 01–02</div><div class="card-ttl c-w">시스템 구축 · 스킬 적용</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bd">
          <ul class="slist">
            <li><div class="si">1</div><div><strong>Claude Design 프로젝트 생성</strong><span>claude.ai/design → 목적·채널 설정</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">2</div><div><strong>토스 디자인 시스템 구조 참고</strong><span>Primitive → Semantic → Component 3계층</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">3</div><div><strong>SKILL.md 추가 지침 업로드</strong><span>bon-animal-card-news v2.0 파일 등록</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">4</div><div><strong>서체 고정</strong><span>Pretendard ExtraBold/Bold/SemiBold/Regular/Light</span></div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag dk">Claude Design</span>
          <span class="tag dk">SKILL.md</span>
          <span class="tag">Pretendard</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-hd green">
          <div class="card-ico">🎨</div>
          <div><div class="card-n on-g">STEP 03</div><div class="card-ttl c-w">브랜드 로고 · 컬러 적용</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bd">
          <ul class="slist">
            <li><div class="si">1</div><div><strong>로고 이미지 첨부</strong><span>원천 컬러 3종 추출 (Light Green / Olive / Warm Brown)</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">2</div><div><strong>컬러 토큰 등록</strong><span>#617d3b · #8B6B4A · #f6d85d 기준 v2.0</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">3</div><div><strong>유형별 배경 조합 고정</strong><span>이벤트·의료정보·공지·신규서비스 4유형</span></div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag ac">브랜드 v2.0</span>
          <span class="tag">컬러 토큰</span>
          <span class="tag">1080×1350px</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-hd warm">
          <div class="card-ico">📌</div>
          <div><div class="card-n on-w">STEP 04</div><div class="card-ttl c-d">핀터레스트 레퍼런스</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bd">
          <ul class="slist">
            <li><div class="si">1</div><div><strong>레퍼런스 이미지 3–5장 선정</strong><span>콘텐츠 유형별 레이아웃·무드 수집</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">2</div><div><strong>슬라이드 텍스트 초안 작성</strong><span>헤딩·본문·CTA 6슬라이드 구성</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">3</div><div><strong>이미지 + 내용 동시 첨부</strong><span>"이 레퍼런스 스타일로 생성해줘" 프롬프트</span></div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Pinterest</span>
          <span class="tag">6슬라이드</span>
          <span class="tag">콘텐츠 기획</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-hd navy">
          <div class="card-ico">🔗</div>
          <div><div class="card-n on-d">STEP 05–06</div><div class="card-ttl c-w">시안 개발 · 플랫폼 전송</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-bd">
          <ul class="slist">
            <li><div class="si">1</div><div><strong>Claude Design 자동 생성</strong><span>분할 생성 (1–2장 → 3–4장 → 5–6장)</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">2</div><div><strong>컬러·폰트 검수</strong><span>구버전 컬러 혼입 여부 확인 후 수정</span></div></li>
            <li><div class="si">3</div><div><strong>Figma 또는 Canva로 전송</strong><span>정밀편집 → Figma MCP / 빠른발행 → Canva MCP</span></div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag dk">Figma MCP</span>
          <span class="tag dk">Canva MCP</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BRAND SYSTEM -->
    <div id="brand" class="sec">
      <div class="sec-dot"></div><div class="sec-title">브랜드 시스템</div>
      <div class="sec-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
      <!-- COLOR -->
      <div class="palette">
